6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both ModernMT and Transifex share a solid foundation of core features including Machine Translation, Translation Memory, Api Access, Real Time. Where ModernMT pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Custom Models, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Transifex uniquely offers Glossary and File Formats and Team Collaboration and Quality Assurance and Cms Integration, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, ModernMT holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Transifex scores 7/10 overall and 6/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Transifex comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while ModernMT begins at $25/mo. Transifex stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. ModernMT requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
