a:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. ModernMT is best suited for translation agencies, LSPs, high volume translation, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Transifex, meanwhile, shines for open source projects, development teams, product localization, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2017, ModernMT describes itself as \"Adaptive machine translation engine that learns from your corrections in real-time.\" Transifex, established in 2009, positions itself as \"Localization platform for developers with continuous integration workflows.\" With 8 years between them, Transifex brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while ModernMT offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
b:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Transifex** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to more features (9 vs 5), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean ModernMT is a poor choice — far from it. ModernMT excels in its own right, particularly for translation agencies and LSPs.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value excellent for continuous localization, go with Transifex. If adapts in real-time to your style matters more to you, ModernMT is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
